---
// The Past Events page is hidden for now. This file is kept on disk (along with
// the markdown in src/content/events/) so it can be brought back later, but it's
// removed from the nav and anyone who hits /past-events is bounced to the home
// page. To re-enable it: delete the redirect below and uncomment the original
// markup, then re-add the nav link in src/components/Nav.astro.
return Astro.redirect("/");
---

